    "description": {
      "zh": "装有一剂L1的一次性无菌注射器，主要成分是去甲肾上腺素。它是用来短期增加力量和耐力的，还可减少疼痛的影响。它将增强生理反应的执行力，比如“该打还是该跑”。增加水分和能量消耗。",
      "en": "A sterile disposable syringe with a dose of L1, based on norepinephrine. It is used for short-term increase of strength and endurance, as well as to reduce the pain effect. This activates the implementation of a physiological response such as \"hit or run\". Increases water and energy consumption."
